          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Combating Implicit Bias in Education Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Education to award competitive grants to local educational agencies to provide training to staff of elementary and secondary schools on implicit bias for purposes of ending discrimination based on such bias, improving the school climate and student-staff relationships, and improving student academic achievement.</p>]]></text>
